# ERP PDF Testing Standard

## Phase
ERP PDF.1 — Production PDF Generation Framework (2026-07-23)

## Playwright Preflight Checklist (before PDF generation)

Every `generatePdf()` call should optionally run a preflight check in CI/testing:

1. Open the private print route (`/print/...?token=...`).
2. Assert HTTP 200.
3. Wait for `document.fonts.ready`.
4. Wait for all `<img>` to load (`networkidle`).
5. Assert `document.title` matches the expected template name.
6. Assert the source record ID is present in the page.
7. Assert no `console.error` entries unrelated to test setup.
8. Assert no horizontal overflow (check `document.documentElement.scrollWidth <= innerWidth`).
9. Assert no elements with `visibility: hidden` that should be visible.
10. Assert expected table row count (where applicable).

## PDF Visual QA Checklist (after generation)

Use Poppler's `pdftoppm` or `pdfimages` to rasterize, then assert:

1. Page count is within expected range.
2. No blank pages (pixel variance > threshold).
3. No near-blank pages.
4. Content does not touch the unsafe margin (15px buffer from edges).
5. Table headers repeat on every page.
6. Totals / signature / approval blocks are not split across pages.
7. Arabic text is correctly shaped (visual snapshot or text extraction).
8. Logo and branding appear on every page.
9. Footer page numbers are correct (Page X of N).
10. No trailing blank page.

## Fixture Coverage Required

| Fixture | Description |
|---|---|
| `fixture-one-row.ts` | 1 data row — minimum table |
| `fixture-25-rows.ts` | 25 rows — standard table |
| `fixture-200-rows.ts` | 200 rows — multi-page |
| `fixture-arabic.ts` | Arabic names, addresses, descriptions |
| `fixture-bilingual.ts` | Mixed Arabic+English in same document |
| `fixture-long-desc.ts` | Very long English description (5000+ chars) |
| `fixture-no-logo.ts` | Missing logo — fallback text |
| `fixture-landscape.ts` | Landscape report |
| `fixture-totals-near-bottom.ts` | Signature block near page boundary |
| `fixture-multi-company.ts` | Two different company branding profiles |
| `fixture-unavailable-gotenberg.ts` | Gotenberg down — expected error |
| `fixture-unauthorized.ts` | No session — expected 401 |
| `fixture-cross-company.ts` | User from company A accessing company B record — expected 403 |

## RLS Test Matrix

| Scenario | Expected Result |
|---|---|
| Authenticated user reads own company PDF history | Pass |
| Authenticated user reads other company PDF history | Blocked |
| Anon reads `erp_generated_pdf_documents` | Blocked |
| Frontend direct insert to `erp_generated_pdf_documents` | Blocked |
| Storage download without permission | Blocked |
| Request to generate with unapproved template | Error: template not approved |

## Test Commands

```bash
# Unit tests
npx vitest run src/lib/pdf/

# E2E (requires Playwright browsers and running app)
npx playwright test tests/pdf/

# PDF rasterization QA (requires Poppler)
pdftoppm -r 150 output/test.pdf /tmp/qa-pages/page

# veraPDF validation (requires Java + veraPDF)
verapdf --flavour 3b --format mrr output/test.pdf > /tmp/verapdf-report.xml
```
